{"version": "2.0","name": "AIMA","subline": "Wordpress Theme","username": "AIWA Design Studio","created": "12/30/2012","website": "http://aiwads.ru","update": "01/29/2015","update_today": true,"email": "info@aiwads.ru","description": "","intro": "Thank you for purchasing our theme. Please feel free for discuss our theme for making best things for this. Enjoy!","button_1_text": "","button_2_text": "","button_3_text": "","button_1_url": "","button_2_url": "","button_3_url": "","sections": [{"title": "Table of Contents","id": "table_of_contents","content": "<p>\tStart Here</p>\n"},{"title": "01 Overview","id": "1_overview","content": "<p style=\"width: 500px; float: left; clear: left; margin: 0px 0px 30px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">\n\tFluxus is a magazine inspired portfolio theme for photographers. It features a horizontal layout, which allows to showcase your art side by side, just like we are used to see it in print. Photographers are very picture oriented, and so is Fluxus. Pay attention to the pictures you are using on this theme and you will be able set up a great portfolio.</p>\n<p style=\"width: 500px; float: left; clear: left; margin: 0px 0px 30px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">\n\tThis documentation explains the theme features, how they work and how to properly use them. If you already know the basis of WordPress based website administration, then everything should be straightforward. Otherwise it is advisable to take a look at some introductory tutorials.</p>\n"},{"title": "02 Installation","id": "2_installation","content": "<h2>\n\tBefore Installation</h2>\n<p>\tIf you never work with Wordpress, please read the standart instruction.</p>\n<ul>\t<li>\t\t<a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Installing_WordPress\">Installing Wordpress</a></li>\n\t<li>\t\t<a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Using_Themes\">Using Themes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\t&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"page-break-after: always;\">\n\t<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<h2>\n\ta. Installation</h2>\n<p>\tAfter Wordpress installation, you must upload AIMA Theme files and activate theme. Theme files can be uploaded in two ways:</p>\n<ol>\n\t<li>\t\t<strong>via FTP:</strong>&nbsp;Navigate to your Wordpress installation directory on server and upload directory with theme files into &nbsp;\n\t\t<pre style=\"display:inline-block;\">\n/wp-content/themes/</pre>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\t\t<strong>via&nbsp;WordPress Theme Uploader:</strong> Login into Wordpress dashboard and select on the left menu&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Appearance &gt; Add New Themes &gt; Upload</strong> and select theme archive file&nbsp;\n\t\t<pre style=\"display:inline-block;\">\naima-wp.zip.</pre>\n\t</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\tAfter successfull theme uploading, you must activate theme. Go to the&nbsp;<strong>Appearance &gt; Themes</strong>, and activete selected theme.</p>\n<h2>\n\tb. Theme Settings</h2>\n<p>\tTheme have a lot off settings. Go to&nbsp;<strong>Appearance &gt; Themes Options.</strong>&nbsp;On this page you can change everythig, including:</p>\n<ul>\t<li>\t\tFavicon;</li>\n\t<li>\t\tSite logo;</li>\n\t<li>\t\tTop bar settings;</li>\n\t<li>\t\tSidebar settings;</li>\n\t<li>\t\tFooter settings;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\tFor choosing different color settings, go to&nbsp;<strong>Appearance &gt; Customize</strong> and select <strong>AIMA Theme Colors</strong> block in Sidebar. You can chage background, main, text, title and link colors. After changing colors, click on <strong>Save &amp; Publish</strong> button.</p>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://aima.tf.aiwads.ru/doc/AIMA_1.3_Theme Color.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://aima.tf.aiwads.ru/doc/AIMA_1.3_Theme%20Color.jpg\" style=\"width: 1024px; height: 556px;\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n\tIf you want go to the default theme color styles - click on changed color block and click on <strong>Default</strong> button for setting default color.</div>\n"},{"title": "3 Setting Up Homepage","id": "setting_up_homepage","content": "<p>\t<span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">Start by creating a new page which will serve as your homepage. Go to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Pages &gt; Add New</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">, set the title and click&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Publish</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">. Now navigate to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Settings &gt; Reading</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">&nbsp;and choose&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">A static page</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">&nbsp;next to the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Front page displays</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">&nbsp;option. From the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Front page</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">&nbsp;select box choose the page that you have just created. Save the changes.</span></p>\n<p>\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\t<span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">Now the page you have just created will act as your homepage. Next thing is to customize it.&nbsp;</span></p>\n"},{"title": "4 Setting Up Blog","id": "setting_up_blog","content": "<p>\t<span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">Crate a new page by going to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Pages &gt; Add New</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">, specify page name and click&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Publish</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">. Now navigate to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Settings &gt; Reading</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">&nbsp;and from the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Posts page</span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">&nbsp;select box choose the page you have just created. Save changes. Now if you visit the page, you should see a list of your blog posts (probably not many at the time).</span></p>\n"},{"title": "5 Setting Up Portfolio","id": "setting_up_portfolio","content": "<p>\tStart Here</p>\n"},{"title": "Navigation Menus","id": "navigation_menus","content": "<p style=\"width: 500px; float: left; clear: left; margin: 0px 0px 30px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">\n\tFluxus theme offers three areas for navigation menus.</p>\n<ol style=\"width: 500px; float: left; clear: left; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">\n\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px;\">\n\t\tHeader Primary Menu&nbsp;<br>\n\t\tMain navigation menu.</li>\n\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px;\">\n\t\tHeader Secondary Menu&nbsp;<br>\n\t\tDisplayed to the right of main menu. It&rsquo;s purpose is to display links that are of less importance.</li>\n\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px;\">\n\t\tFooter Primary Menu&nbsp;<br>\n\t\tDisplayed on the right side of the footer.</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"width: 500px; float: left; clear: left; margin: 0px 0px 30px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 'Droid Serif', georgia, serif; font-size: medium; line-height: 30px;\">\n\tGo to&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; position: static; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-family: 'Droid Sans', arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.901961) 0px 0px 1px; padding: 2px 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline-block; border-radius: 2px; background: rgb(234, 234, 234);\">Appearance &gt; Menus</span>&nbsp;and add previously created Homepage, Portfolio and Blog pages to the main navigation menu.</p>\n"},{"title": "03 Portfolio","id": "3_portfolio","content": "<p>\tStart Here</p>\n"}],"use_sub": true,"logo": "http://aiwads.ru/wp-content/themes/pitch-wp-v1.3.1/images/newLogo.png","favicon": "http://aiwads.ru/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/favicon.ico","customcss": "","easing": "swing","easingduration": "500","bgimage": "","bgrepeat": "repeat","bgattachment": "scroll","bgcolor": "EFEFEF","textcolor": "1C140D","linkcolor": "889C48","hrcolor1": "CCCCCC","hrcolor2": "FFFFFF","btncolor": "FFFFFF","btncolor1": "CBE86B","btncolor2": "889C48","sidebarbgimage": "","sidebarbgrepeat": "repeat","sidebarbgcolor": "FFFFFF","sidebartextcolor": "1C140D","sidebarlinkcolor": "1C140D","sidebaractivecolor": "CBE86B","sidebaractivetextcolor": "1C140D","sidebarhrcolor1": "D1C9C2","sidebarhrcolor2": "FFF6ED","cufon": "","documentationttype": "bootstrap","itemURL": "","sendJSON": "","sendZIP": "","sendPWD": ""}
